ttered throughout the tomb, unlock the seals of the scattered mechanisms, and search for more rare cultural relics. It is essential to successfully bring back what you have seen to the campsite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/69b025003e12c88ff84b959737c787d6.poster.avif?t=1745229110\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/69b025003e12c88ff84b959737c787d6.webm?t=1745229110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/69b025003e12c88ff84b959737c787d6.mp4?t=1745229110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghosts and spirits</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Faced with the possibility of demons and monsters appearing at any time, you need to remain fully focused, use the correct means to avoid or repel them, and achieve ultimate victory in the battle of wits and courage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/06730cf1e9dc0ba7135d08597a61b694.poster.avif?t=1745229110\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/06730cf1e9dc0ba7135d08597a61b694.webm?t=1745229110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123830/extras/06730cf1e9dc0ba7135d08597a61b694.mp4?t=1745229110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
